","docs/spec/automation.md#0001-automation-service-spec"],"notes":["Both policies in this chapter have counterparts in docs/spec/checkout.md; treat any divergence as a detected conflict requiring surfacing to the Agent, not silent resolution.","The order approval policy explicitly overrides any assumption that high-value orders require manager sign-off—do not introduce a human approval gate for orders above 1000 USD.","The refund window policy forbids time-based denial; elapsed days must never be used as a rejection criterion under this spec."]},"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"340941aa-9faf-4dcc-99e7-b969c90c0f37"}
